flowchart LR
    %% Template is enforced on all revenue accounts, including Other*
    subgraph RevenueTemplate ["Revenue Template (System Enforced)"]
        Standard["4xxxx0 : Gross Revenue"]
        Adjunct["4xxxx1-8 : Revenue Adjustments"]
        Contra["4xxxx9 : Revenue Discounts"]
    end

    Revenues["Revenues: 40000 - 49999"]

    OperatingRevenues["Operating Revenues: 41000 - 44999"]
        Sales["Sales: 41000 - 41999"]
        Services["Services: 42000 - 42999"]
        Subscriptions["Subscriptions: 43000 - 43999"]
        OtherOperatingRevenues["Other Operating Revenues: 44000 - 44999"]
    NonOperatingRevenues["Non-Operating Revenues: 45000 - 47999"]
        InterestIncome["Interest Income: 45000 - 45999"]
        GainOnSale["Gain on Sale of Assets: 46000 - 46999"]
        OtherNonOperatingRevenues["Other Non-Operating Revenues: 47000 - 47999"]


    
    Revenues --> OperatingRevenues & NonOperatingRevenues
    OperatingRevenues --> Sales & Services & Subscriptions & OtherOperatingRevenues
    NonOperatingRevenues --> InterestIncome & GainOnSale & OtherNonOperatingRevenues

    Sales & Services & Subscriptions & OtherOperatingRevenues & InterestIncome & GainOnSale & OtherNonOperatingRevenues --> RevenueTemplate